'''Stephen Youll''' (born [[June 8]], [[1960s#1965|1965]]) is the cover artist for many science fiction and fantasy books. His twin brother, [[Paul Youll]], has also contributed to several ''[[Star Wars]]'' books.

==''Star Wars'' bibliography==
