*''[[Tales from Jabba's Palace]]'' - [[1995]]
*''[[Tales of the Bounty Hunters]]'' - [[1996]]
*''[[Star Wars: Tales (Omnibus)|Star Wars: Tales]]'' - [[1997]]
*[[The Bounty Hunter Wars]] trilogy
**''[[The Mandalorian Armor]]'' - 1997
**''[[Slave Ship]]'' - ''[[1998]]''
**''[[Hard Merchandise]]'' - 1998

